# Recommended ignores for projects using bedrock for knowledge management.
# Keep or remove the local pointer based on your repo policy.

# If bedrock is a symlink, many teams keep the pointer tracked.
# If you prefer it untracked, uncomment the next line.
# bedrock/

# Usually ignore noisy generated or transient knowledge branches.
bedrock/Evidence/
bedrock/Outputs/
bedrock/.obsidian/workspace*.json
bedrock/.obsidian/cache/
